val two = 1 + 1
不变量（val）
你不能改变这个不变量的值.

可变量 var

abstract class can't not be instanced




traits
similar to interfaces in java
traits -> state variables
       -> methods with implementations

scala -> abstract(abstraction in the common hierarchy) vs
         traits(provide specifications)

abstract
Eg. files -> normal files, compressed, encrypted,...
    Accounts, Savings, Current, Trading,...


traits
Eg. tv remote -> red, blue, green, vol +/-, ch +/-, ...
    sony tv -> red will show the date

In Java:
interface TVRemote {
    public void onRed();
    ...
    }
In scala:
trait TVRemote {
    def onRed():Unit = {}
    ...
    }